<p>Your local business just lost visibility. Not because of a bad review or a weak listing. Google AI Overviews changed how local search results appear, and most business owners have not noticed yet.</p>
<p>The ai overviews local search impact is measurable. Organic click-through rates dropped 58% for top-ranking pages when AI summaries appear. AI local packs now show 1 to 2 businesses instead of 3. And 88% of local markets tracked by <a href="https://www.sterlingsky.ca/the-state-of-local-seo-in-2026/">Sterling Sky</a> lost business visibility in the transition.</p>
<p>These numbers are not projections. They come from studies by Ahrefs, Semrush, Seer Interactive, and Local Falcon across hundreds of thousands of queries.</p>
<p>We publish 3,500+ blog posts and local SEO content pieces across 70+ industries. We track these changes because they affect every client we serve. This data study compiles the most current findings on how AI Overviews reshape local search.</p>
<p>Here is what you will learn:</p>
<ul>
<li>How many local queries now trigger AI Overviews</li>
